---
title: Tex-Mex Style Double Beef and Pork Rice Skillet with Sweet Bell Peppers and Cheddar Cheese
description: Cheese lovers, this one is for you! Succulent beef and pork mix is seasoned with our Mexican Seasoning in a hearty rice skillet with ooey-gooey cheddar cheese on top.  A bonus delight comes from the deliciously crispy skillet bits at the bottom of the pan. May your cheese pulls be long and your meal time enjoyable!
